data.title: Greenbriar Crossing
data.meta_description: Greenbriar Crossing new townhomes for sale in Webster Village. Spacious luxury ranch townhomes, featuring open floor plans
data.text:
Discover Tranquil Luxury at Greenbriar Crossing:

New Ranch Townhomes For Sale in Webster Village.

Welcome to Greenbriar Crossing, where effortless living meets contemporary style. Nestled in Webster Village, our community offers the perfect blend of convenience, comfort, and luxury.

Tour our captivating model townhome and envision yourself residing in one of our 124 thoughtfully designed residences.

Luxury Ranch Townhomes

Unwind in your private oasis:

Spacious ranch-style design: Experience single-level living with our modern ranch townhomes, featuring open floor plans and abundant natural light.

Luxury finishes at every turn: Embrace Pride Marks signature craftsmanship, from hardwood floors and Wellborn cabinets to stunning lighting packages and gas fireplaces.

Your personal touch awaits: Collaborate with Inde Design Studios experts to curate your dream kitchen, baths, and closets, reflecting your unique style.

Beyond your doorstep, a vibrant community thrives:

Community Center: Host memorable gatherings in our dedicated entertaining space, perfect for neighborhood events or private celebrations.

Stay fit and connect: Get energized in our fitness center, and enjoy the camaraderie of your neighbors.

Effortless living: Leave the worries behind with full-service HOA maintenance encompassing all exterior upkeep, allowing you to simply savor life.
